Benefits of Parquet/Columnar format: 
0. Ref: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DxAuj_Ky5aw
1. Creates files according to columns, e.g if there are 5 columns there will be 5 underneath files.
2. Schema follows along with data.
3. It has builtin compression and metadata about what is in the columns. 
4. It stores info like count, min, max values as metadata enabling queries to be faster.
5. It supports predicate pushdown e.g if you are searching for date range filter it can eliminate the scan.
